**Ikenberry & Kupchan, ’10**
[G. John Ikenberry, Professor of Politics & International Affairs @ Princeton, Charles A. Kupchan, Professor of International Affairs @ Georgetown, Senior Fellow @ The Council on Foreign Relations, “A New Japan, a New Asia,” January 21st 2010, 
